description: Guess who’s back and excited to fuck some more Sean Cody ass! That’s right, the adorable Parker. And the willing bottom? That’ll be Randy. “I’m gonna go meet up with Randy in a little bit and fuck the shit out of him! I’m excited about that. He’s a big dude, but I’m gonna be the dominant one…” Oh, and that he was! After throwing a football around to warm up for the real thing, they went back to the house to get to business. Big-dicked Randy took it like a champ, moans and groans and all! Parker definitely missed us...
title: Parker & Randy: Bareback
